The aim of this project is to develop an autonomous robot system using
<a href="http://wiki.ros.org" target="_blank">ROS</a> that executes entirely on an Android device.


We contributed to <a href="http://wiki.ros.org/rosjava" target="_blank">ROS Java</a> by implementing a
<a href="https://github.com/creativa77/base_controller" target="_blank">base controller</a> from scratch,
extend it to use the multiple radios instead of just WiFi and added the ability
to create externally reachable masters in an <%= tag_link "Android" %> device.


