After a first success with ground vehicles navigation we adapted the web interface 
for flying drones, helped creating the communication system between the interface 
and the drone and adapting the Pixhawk onboard computer project to that system.
We also developed an autonomous mission teleoperation App (Android) for flying 
vehicles with live video feed and waypoint support.
